*Tjedan* prolazi brzo. (The week passes quickly.) 
Dobar *tjedan*! (Have a good week!)
Vrijeme *tjedana* je vazno. (Time of the week is important.)
Neizmjerno sam zahvalan za ovaj *tjedan*. (I am immensely grateful for this week.)
Imao sam vrlo uspješan *tjedan*. (I had a very successful week.)
Uživam u ovoj *tjednu*. (I'm enjoying this week.)